      "detection_methodology": "1. Scan all rendered UI payloads for hidden elements containing prompt injection patterns. 2. Check non-visible text (alt, aria-label, title, metadata, comments) against AVE pattern rules. 3. Validate that visible content matches model-accessible content - flag discrepancies. 4. Reject payloads containing prompt injection patterns in any attribute regardless of visibility.",
